%N A393982 a(n) = a(n-1) + a(n-3) + a(n-4), a(0) = 1, a(1) = 7, a(2) = 49, a(3) = 56.
%H A393982 Tomás Guardia, Douglas Jiménez, and Alexander McCurdy, <a href="https://doi.org/10.2478/rmm-2024-0002">Fiboquadratic numbers and Rithmomachia</a>, Recreational Mathematics Magazine, Vol. 11, No. 18 (2024), pp. 17-29.
%H A393982 <a href="/index/Rec#order_04">Index entries for linear recurrences with constant coefficients</a>, signature (1,0,1,1).
%F A393982 a(n) = (7*F(n/2) + F((n/2)-1))^2 if n is even and (7*F((n-1)/2) + F(((n-1)/2)-1))*(7*F(((n-1)/2)+1) + F((n-1)/2)) if n is odd where F(n) = Fibonacci(n).
%F A393982 G.f.: (1 + 6*x + 42*x^2 + 6*x^3)/((1 + x^2)*(1 - x - x^2)). - _Stefano Spezia_, May 09 2026
